The paper discusses the use of automatic differentiation in machine learning, which is a subfield of computer science focused on developing algorithms that can learn from and make predictions on data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of automatic differentiation in numerical analysis (cs.NA), software engineering (cs.SE), control systems (cs.SY), and computational engineering (cs.CE), which are all relevant to the topic of the paper.
